@startuml
hide empty description

title ReviewRun State Machine (Positive Selection)

[*] --> Created

Created --> Open : openRun()
Open --> CollectingSelections : beginSelectionWindow()
CollectingSelections --> Evaluating : closeSelectionWindow()
Evaluating --> Completed : finalizeSelectedCandidates()
Completed --> Superseded : startNewRunFromSameDelivery()

' Optional fast-path when no review window is needed.
Open --> Evaluating : immediateEvaluation()

note right of CollectingSelections
Reviewers add positive SelectionMarks.
No mark != rejection.
end note

note right of Evaluating
Selection policy can retain images with
>= 1 positive mark (or stricter thresholds).
end note

note right of Superseded
Superseded keeps historical traceability;
it does not imply invalid outcomes.
end note

@enduml
